Main Tasks And Responsibilities

Noesis is looking for candidates with the following profile:


Drive the design and evolution of cutting-edge data and AI solutions, leveraging Databricks and GCP to enable scalable, governed, and intelligent analytics capabilities;
Own and enhance the semantic layer and certified business metrics, ensuring high-quality, trusted data products that empower analytics and AI Agents across the organization;
Transform data into strategic business impact by applying advanced causal inference techniques and Generative AI approaches to uncover actionable insights and support data-driven decision-making;
